reviews.name: HP 75 Tri-color Original Ink Cartridge
reviews.reviewText: i only buy these cartridges, but i would like to pay a little less as i am using them so quickly with very minimal printing...so i do buy more often, i would rather pay around 10-12 dollars,20 is a little high
reviews.title: good ink!

reviews.name: HP 75 Tri-color Original Ink Cartridge
reviews.reviewText: I really enjoy this inkjet as it makes beautiful pictures and great documents. I have received compliments on both and HP never lets me down. Great job! I recommend this product to everyone.
reviews.title: Ink jet

reviews.name: HP 75 Tri-color Original Ink Cartridge
reviews.reviewText: I use a great amount of color ink and would really like to see WalMart carry the HP 75XL inkjet cartridge. It is a far better value and eliminates the need for frequent cartridge changes.
reviews.title: HP 75 Tri-color inkjet cartridge

reviews.name: HP 75 Tri-color Original Ink Cartridge
reviews.reviewText: When using HP ink cartridges I have found that they are not empty when the printer gives you a warning. I continue to use my cartridges until it actually does not print anymore. I think of all the cartridges I threw out that still had ink left in them - I discovered this when reading an article years ago.
reviews.title: Don't Believe Empty Cartridge Warning

reviews.name: HP 75 Tri-color Original Ink Cartridge
reviews.reviewText: Very good product and is easy to install so i recommend HP ink.
reviews.title: Ink
